      "id": "1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Get up and running with AkiraDocs in minutes."
    },
    {
      "id": "2",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Quick Deploy",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Option 1: Deploy with Vercel",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "The fastest way to get started is using Vercel:"
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "[![Deploy with Vercel](https://vercel.com/button)](https://vercel.com/new/clone?repository-url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FCloud-Code-AI%2Fakiradocs-template)"
    },
    {
      "id": "6",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Option 2: Using CLI",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Create a new project using our CLI:"
    },
    {
      "id": "8",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npx create-akiradocs@latest my-docs",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Basic Setup Steps",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "10",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "1. <strong>Clone the Repository</strong> (if not using Quick Deploy)"
    },
    {
      "id": "11",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "git clone https://github.com/your-org/akira-docs-template\ncd akira-docs-template",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "12",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "2. <strong>Install Dependencies</strong>"
    },
    {
      "id": "13",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npm install\n# or\nyarn install",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "14",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "3. <strong>Start Development Server</strong>"
    },
    {
      "id": "15",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npm run dev\n# or\nyarn dev",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "16",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "4. Open `http://localhost:3000` in your browser"
    },
    {
      "id": "17",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Initial Configuration",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "18",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "1. <strong>Update Site Configuration</strong>\nEdit `akiradocs.config.json`:"
    },
    {
      "id": "19",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "{\n  \"site\": {\n    \"title\": \"Your Docs\",\n    \"description\": \"Your documentation description\"\n  }\n}",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "json",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "20",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "2. <strong>Configure Translation</strong> (Optional)"
    },
    {
      "id": "21",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "{\n  \"translation\": {\n    \"auto_translate\": true,\n    \"provider\": \"anthropic\",\n    \"targetLanguages\": [\"es\", \"fr\", \"de\"]\n  }\n}",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "json",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    }
  ]
}